message.body: Lindsey, I will definitely try to get my ass down to your studio tomorrow. Would love to come down and write; just trying to get the other bullshit outta the way today. I'll check in with you tomorrow morning.
Hells yeah! No pressure if you aren't feeling it but it would be fun! Check me in the AM! Have a good night!
Will do; thanks. If I can't come tomorrow, I will next week.
